snippet.title: Tales Of Destruction Update Trailer - RETOOLED
snippet.description:
The latest update, Tales Of Destruction is now out!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1997590/RETOOLED/

Feature highlights:
- Tales, new level: Distribution Hub
- Weapon alt fire options
- High score & rank systems
- And much more, full patch notes over on steam!
